        "1427": {
          "vnum": 1427,
          "name": "Cart Path's End",
          "description": "There's something sparkly in the air here. You can still smell a whiff of the Chardaleth Sea, kelpy and briny, and Cium Nustrum's cologne, musky and feral, but you can't shake the feeling you're in for something new. A cart path returns to the country road to the north, and to the south you see a riverbed.",
