        "1434": {
          "vnum": 1434,
          "name": "Barn",
          "description": "The creaking draws your eyes upward to the barn rafters. A thick rope has been knotted to a support beam, the weight and movement of its burden straining that beam. The rope swings back and forth, providing a panoramic view of a hanging man, his ashen face, crooked neck, and limp form. Spittle and a touch of blood color his lower lip.",
