        "3068": {
          "vnum": 3068,
          "name": "Farmhouse",
          "description": "With a grunt, you force the door open. A few flies buzz about. You see a cooking area but smell no grease or victuals. A hanging tapestry divides the rest of house into two: a connubial area with a firm bed and abundant pillows, and a child's area with a cot and lovingly hand-crafted wooden horses, pigs, and cows strewn about.",
